L’Oreal SA (OR)  heiress Liliane
Bettencourt,  France ’s third-richest person, will seek a
suspension of a ruling that she is mentally unfit to manage her
own affairs, Jean-Rene Farthouat, her lawyer, said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
